;ModelName: ; Each line in this file contains data on the decos in the directories
; under this directory.  Comment lines begin with a ";" and will be ignored.
; The format of each line is:
; ModelName - The name of the model.  This is the value given to the "model" tag
;             that was assigned when the entity was inserted into the map.
; PathName  - The path of the .dkm file
; SolidType - Either "bbox" or "not".  Do not include quotes.
; Mass-       The mass of the deco.  1.0 is the same as player mass
; Exploding - 1 if the deco can be destroyed
PathName: 0 if the deco can not be destroyed.

;ModelName: ; HitPoints - If the deco can be destroyed
PathName: this is the amount of damage it can take.
Max* - These fields specify the size of the object.

;ModelName: ; GibType   - Type of gibs this thing throws off when beaten down.

SolidType: WHITE.... default value is 0 (which means it doesn't explode)

;ModelName: ; AnimSeq   - Number of animation sequences this deco has.  For decos with only one frame
; seq0-seq4 - frames or frame sequences of animation  use "-" for a set of frames use "~" to loop the frames
